cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.CL. 

The paper discusses a tool that generates and interprets deep links to desktop resources, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of RDF to interlink deep links with other resources also suggests a connection to data management (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the use of HTML representation of resources and links to follow suggests a possible connection to web technologies (cs.DL).
